            <title>[SEC-146] LDAPS Support does not work</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-146</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In order to use the LDAP feature for authentication and authorization over SSL I had to modify the class :&lt;br/&gt;
 org.acegisecurity.providers.ldap.DefaultInitialDirContextFactory&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At line 132 I have modified the test:&lt;br/&gt;
if (url.startsWith(&quot;ldap:&quot;)) {&lt;br/&gt;
By:&lt;br/&gt;
if (url.startsWith(&quot;ldap:&quot;) || url.startsWith(&quot;ldaps:&quot;)) {&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That&apos;s the only way I&apos;ve been able to do it after a long debugging session.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I hope it will help.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Franck&lt;/p&gt;</description>
